snippet.title: Dream Warrior trailer
snippet.description:
The Demon Lord is going to destroy the world, as you'd expect. Not everyone can be the hero, though. You, for example, are the town drunk. Can you save the world anyway?

Check out Dream Warrior on Steam and Itch!
